    //
    // Frontend code MUST NOT import:
    //   - client SDK initialiser
    //   - firebase/firestore (client Firestore SDK)
    //   - firebase/auth     (client Auth SDK)
    //   - firebase/storage  (client Storage SDK)
    //
    // These rules act as a full safety net — any accidental
